Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard; an island with \Ntwo parts, one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After forming an alliance with Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally encountered Caesar Clown
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but was beaten by his mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Law, too, got taken down by \Nthe Navy G-5 base commander - Vergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what I'm going to do is give Smiley,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the weapon from four \Nyears ago, a big "boost."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will add a new effect to the poison gas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the weapon of mass destruction \Nwill reach completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new weapon that will make \Nits debut today is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! I see a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley! I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Smiley?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy, Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Deadliest Weapon of Mass \NDestruction in History! Shinokuni!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that creature?!\N--Doesn't it look like those creepy jellies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can he be reborn as?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect weapon of mass destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a big frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out! Something's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "something"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know?! But I'm \Nsure it's something bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as the Master \Nsays and run to the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't believe the \Nsled broke! Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting strange since he ate the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the candy was that good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even soldiers from this island \Nare running desperately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't agree more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weapon of mass destruction - Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the face of the island completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's happening?!\N--I don't know! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem with the last experiment \Nwas there were survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could still move even after being \Npoisoned so they were able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I should've petrified them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gas clings to people's bodies like ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It enters through their skin and \Nparalyzes their whole body at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the perfect weapon of \Nmass destruction, Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a good glimpse of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...solidifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something out of a horror movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who just died looked \Nlike Caesar's men...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that purple smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where are they filming this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know yet, you \Nbetter not turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That was happening on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We have to run! Or \Nwe'll end up like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere to run on \Nthe island from such gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! That's why \Nthey sealed off the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't want the gas to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn! This is not joke! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard, you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still breathing but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's badly wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're okay thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gastanet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's pull him out from \Nunder this iron pipe, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be so disappointed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be pretty heavy physical work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It won't budge an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pull you out soon! \NHang in there, Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…kick the bucket yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That asshole - Caesar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to save my crew first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I can't die in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta get to the lab where my \Ncrew are as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're hurt all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we all wanna go to the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save those \Nkids from that jerk, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you join forces with \Nus and beat that gas bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that? It's \Na huge amount of smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't look like just smoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Poison gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey hey! What should do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no no! What do you want \Nme to do about that smoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's just go to the...\N--You two, get on my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna reach us soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, run at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anybody gets caught, \Nwe'll have to leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-san, it's gonna catch \Nus if we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dead! It's catching up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run faster than the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we outrun it even a little bit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't turn around! Just focus \Non running at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't run like this for very long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a mysterious animal up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A dragon!\N--A dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! A dragon is a mythical creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They exist on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that one is way smaller \Nthan the one I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! If we can catch \Nit, we can fly on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I can't run like this any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's Zoro and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're being chased by the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon!--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, why are they running like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai-san got his whole body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! He's not gonna let \Nme have those legs, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin! That's not important now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! That smoke is \Ndeadly! You have to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... I can't even raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Sea Prism Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your friends, "Straw Hat Luffy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I'd expect from \Nyour friends - they're tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But soon they're going to be running \Nout of breath and poisoned by the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually, there'll be only an \Nuninhabitable "Land of Death (Shinokuni)"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one outside of this \Nlaboratory will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither will any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now prove it to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before this weapon of mass \Ndestruction - Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pirate with a 400 million berry bounty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Navy vice admiral,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even a Warlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are totally helpless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...against the tide of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna do something \Nto Luffy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help but I'd be easily \Ncaught with these wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the formula for \Nthe drug that I found
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sedatives I got will be wasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't do anything"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wrote this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! A cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Smo-yan!\N--Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief! They're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But they're still held captive!\N--Damn! So we're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan! Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that laboratory is really well-built!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can easily carry big \Nequipment with this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can you two be so relaxed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... Okay, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unexpected to see Vergo \Nhere but Straw Hat-ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't miss a beat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess it up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it garners attention all across the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Straw Hats finally come face to face with Shinokuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when the crew's annihilation is all but guaranteed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law's life-or-death plan is set in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Launching the Counter Attack! \NLuffy and Law's Great Escape!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
